WEBVTT

00:01.825 --> 00:04.456
Why would we get her back
just to lose her again?

00:04.696 --> 00:07.781
Previously on <i>Fringe...</i>

00:07.816 --> 00:10.767
You must face this pain
together.

00:10.785 --> 00:12.769
The pain is her legacy
to you both.

00:12.787 --> 00:14.488
It's proof
that she was here.

00:14.539 --> 00:16.740
Our daughter dedicated
her life to freeing us.

00:16.774 --> 00:18.342
And now we're gonna
dedicate ours

00:18.376 --> 00:20.661
to making sure that
that means something.

00:20.712 --> 00:22.546
You got that look
on your face.

00:22.581 --> 00:23.506
What look?

00:23.531 --> 00:25.115
The look that says,
"I'm worried about you."

00:25.116 --> 00:26.467
Should I be?

00:26.501 --> 00:28.502
What have you done?

00:28.553 --> 00:29.887
The tech that gave them

00:29.921 --> 00:31.622
their advantage over us--
I have it now.

00:31.640 --> 00:34.241
You implanted one
in yourself?

00:34.276 --> 00:36.393
It gives me enough information
to determine

00:36.428 --> 00:38.329
their probable futures.

00:38.363 --> 00:42.283
We're going to avenge Etta.
Windmark's next.

