01:24.609 --> 01:27.444
Sorry I'm late.
That's okay.

01:30.398 --> 01:31.899
Where'd you get it?

01:31.950 --> 01:36.019
Let's just say it was
a souvenir for one of my men.

01:36.037 --> 01:39.156
And this identical to the one
that Peter used on himself?

01:39.190 --> 01:41.191
<i>Yeah, from the base</i>
<i>of the cranium.</i>

01:41.209 --> 01:44.078
So how is it activated?
I'm not sure.

01:44.129 --> 01:45.629
If Dr. Bishop finds out,

01:45.664 --> 01:49.049
we'd love to learn
anything we can about it.

01:49.084 --> 01:53.504
Olivia, if I had any inclination
of what Peter was doing...

01:53.538 --> 01:57.040
I know.

02:00.762 --> 02:03.147
Astrid said you were
getting low on ammunition.

02:03.181 --> 02:07.267
The resistance just raided
a weapons depot in Midtown.

02:07.318 --> 02:09.553
Take these for now.

02:09.571 --> 02:12.606
We'll arrange a meet
for more later.

02:12.657 --> 02:14.825
I've got to go.

02:14.859 --> 02:17.894
If there's anything else
I can do to help...

02:17.912 --> 02:19.896
Thank you, Anil.

03:43.615 --> 03:46.667
There.

04:21.452 --> 04:24.204
He is foretelling
your movements.

04:25.757 --> 04:29.626
<i>He has gained the ability</i>
<i>to run futures.</i>

